 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sky-Ferreira-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sky-Ferreira-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sky-Ferreira-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/sky-ferreira">斯凯·费雷拉（Sky Ferreira）</a>对纽约市的一个广告牌做出了回应，该广告牌声称她被唱片公司“扣为人质”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/sky-ferreira-cover-interview-2022-masochism-3249551">斯凯·费雷拉（Sky Ferreira）：“我开始意识到：我很高兴我听起来像我”</a></strong></li></ul><p>据报道，费雷拉的歌迷在时代广场买了一个广告牌，分享这位歌手的照片，上面写着“Free Sky Ferreira”，声称她的音乐被她的唱片公司 Capitol Records 劫持。</p><p>这位歌手对广告牌和消息做出了回应，在她的 Instagram 故事中发布了一张照片，并配上标题“这是真的”，确认她的唱片公司阻止她发布新音乐，尤其是她 2013 年首张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-sky-ferreira-15148-313075">《Night Time》</a>的后续作品。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-sky-ferreira-15148-313075">，我的时间</a>。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> Sky Ferreira 确实证实她被自己的品牌扣为人质<a href="https://t.co/UAjPZzMWee">pic.twitter.com/UAjPZzMWee</a></p><p> — #freeskyferreira (@ssskyferreira) <a href="https://twitter.com/ssskyferreira/status/1692103930010845235?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 8 月 17 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>该广告牌似乎是由这位歌手的 Instagram 粉丝帐户组织的，自 2021 年 3 月以来，该歌手一直在为费雷拉从她的唱片公司释放而开展活动。自 2015 年以来，他们一直在阻止她的第二张专辑《Masochism》的发行，”Instagram 帐户上的置顶帖子中<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/Cky5zEBrxjx/?img_index=1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">写道</a>。</p><p>今年早些时候，费雷拉<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sky-ferreira-says-the-lack-of-her-new-music-is-beyond-fucked-up-3380755">谈到了她在推出新音乐时所面临的困难以及她作为“难搞”艺术家的名声</a>。</p><p> 1 月 14 日，她在<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/CnZy8tqA0ts/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a>上分享了一段新音乐片段，并配文：“我想把它发布出去”。在她的故事中，她<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/B0r9UDiBygU/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">分享了</a>一段她在 2019 年试音时表演这首未发行歌曲的片段。“看看日期，”她在附图中写道。 “我很久以前就试图发行这首歌。这不是我的错，也不是阴谋或其他什么。” </p><figure id="attachment_3484610" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3484610" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3484610" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sky-Ferreira-on-stage.jpg" alt="Sky Ferreira 将于 2022 年 6 月 30 日在丹麦罗斯基勒举行的第 50 届罗斯基勒音乐节上表演。图片来源：Rune Hellestad-Corbis/Corbis via Getty" width="2000" height="2487" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sky-Ferreira-on-stage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sky-Ferreira-on-stage-400x497.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sky-Ferreira-on-stage-800x995.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sky-Ferreira-on-stage-696x865.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sky-Ferreira-on-stage-1392x1731.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sky-Ferreira-on-stage-1068x1328.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3484610" class="wp-caption-text"> Sky Ferreira 将于 2022 年 6 月 30 日在丹麦罗斯基勒举行的第 50 届罗斯基勒音乐节上表演。图片来源：Rune Hellestad-Corbis/Corbis via Getty</figcaption></figure><p>她继续说道：“我不是一个歇斯底里/撒谎/懒惰的疯子。我也可以拉起2014年未发行单曲的表演。这太操蛋了。我对此感到非常沮丧。</p><p> “‘难相处’或‘高度紧张’并不意味着人们有权损害和阻碍我的职业生涯，”她写道。 “我的处境很困难，我必须‘困难’才能度过难关。 I have to protect my work &amp; myself somehow?</p><p> “A lot of it is not being allowed to say or do anything I want/need without it being dismissed. I can&#39;t think of a time in the last 7 years where I&#39;ve been able to just focus on what I&#39;m supposed to do, despite having to basically sacrifice every aspect of my life to make sure it happens.</p><p> “It&#39;s not okay. If I&#39;m not allowed to say something without consequence &amp; the people who are supposed to do their job refuse to look out for me… How am I not going to be &#39;difficult&#39;?!?”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/sky-ferreira-cover-interview-2022-masochism-3249551">In an interview with <em>NME</em> last year</a> , the singer revealed that her highly anticipated second album was nearly done. “It&#39;s basically done for the most part, it&#39;s just that some parts need to be re-recorded, Just the finishing touches, really,” she said.</p><p> &#39;Masochism&#39; was first scheduled for release in 2015, and has been pushed back multiple times since. In October 2021, she said a <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sky-ferreira-teases-new-music-set-to-arrive-in-march-3084718">release date for the album had been confirmed</a> , teasing its arrival for March 2022. </p><figure id="attachment_3484615" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3484615" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3484615" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sky-Ferreira-performing-1.jpg" alt="Sky Ferreira performs onstage during the 2019 Pitchfork Music Festival at Union Park on July 19, 2019 in Chicago, Illinois. Credit: Barry Brecheisen/GETTY" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sky-Ferreira-performing-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sky-Ferreira-performing-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sky-Ferreira-performing-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sky-Ferreira-performing-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sky-Ferreira-performing-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Sky-Ferreira-performing-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3484615" class="wp-caption-text"> Sky Ferreira performs onstage during the 2019 Pitchfork Music Festival at Union Park on July 19, 2019 in Chicago, Illinois. Credit: Barry Brecheisen/GETTY</figcaption></figure><p> The following month, she <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sky-ferreira-says-new-album-is-actually-coming-out-in-2022-3121685">asserted that &#39;Masochism&#39; was “actually coming out”</a> in 2022, and back in January 2022, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sky-ferreiras-mother-says-her-daughters-new-album-is-coming-in-march-3144844">Ferreira&#39;s mother re-confirmed that a March release was on the cards</a> .</p><p> When the album wasn&#39;t released in March, Ferreira told fans to <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sky-ferreira-reveals-death-threats-and-that-second-album-has-been-delayed-3195242">hold off on their “wrath and death threats”</a> until the following month.</p><p> The singer also <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sky-ferreira-sexism-music-industry-3300176">opened up about her experiences with sexism in the music industry</a> and how she&#39;s resisted attempts to pigeonhole or control her image throughout her career.</p><p> “In the music industry, everyone&#39;s trying to mold you. They have an idea of what you should be,” she said in a conversation with <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nancy-sinatra">Nancy Sinatra</a> for <a href="https://www.interviewmagazine.com/music/sky-ferreira-tells-nancy-sinatra-about-her-penchant-for-pain" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Interview</em></a> . “People get greedy. When I was younger, I got cornered in situations where it was like, &#39;You have to do this,&#39; and I didn&#39;t know better. It was just different back then.”</p><p> She continued: “The internet was there, but it wasn&#39;t this thing that people had figured out. I used it to my advantage – that really helped me get my stuff out. But I&#39;ve been shelved so many times. You know, I first came out when I was 15 and it wasn&#39;t a fair representation of me. And then, I wasn&#39;t even that much older, but I started meeting people to collaborate with, and it started falling into place.</p><p> Ferreira&#39;s highly anticipated LP, &#39;Masochism&#39;, is still yet to receive a formal release date. Her latest release was 2022&#39;s <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-sky-ferreiras-first-new-song-in-over-three-years-dont-forget-3233906">&#39;Don&#39;t Forget&#39;</a> .</p><p></p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sky-ferreira-responds-to-billboard-claims-of-being-held-hostage-by-label-3484571">Sky Ferreira responds to billboard claims of being “held hostage” by label</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
